Class PlatformDeploymentProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.RelationshipProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.assets.infrastructure.PlatformDeploymentProperties
public class PlatformDeploymentProperties extends RelationshipProperties
PlatformDeploymentProperties describes the properties for the SoftwareServerPlatformDeployment relationship between a Software Server Platform and a Host.
